  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK209">
<l>taṉṉaittāṉ kātala ṉāyi ṉeṉaittoṉṟun</l>
<l>tuṉṉaṟka tīviṉaip pāl</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If a man love himself, let him not commit any sin however small.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
